    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process by which electrons are lost from or transferred to neutral molecules or atoms to form positively or negatively charged particles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
